snippet.title: NARCISSIST ESSAYS
snippet.description:
This collection of essays is our most curious questions when we have experienced narcissitic abuse. It is to understand narcissistic abuse in depth to aid our recovery. I am told I communicate my experience with narcissism very well & understand the narcissistic personality disordered mind. I use my experiences, knowledge & understanding to make it make sense.

My grandmother & mother have NPD. My ex husband of 10 years is a narcissist & we have 2 son's. My upbringing made me a magnet for narcissistic/toxic people until I learned of narcissistic abuse age 37. I am no contact with many people & meeting my true self for the first time. It is the happiest I have ever been. 

With encouragement from my therapist I have found a platform to share with others. Sending you lots love & strength.

Udate Oct 2021; great news! My essays have been selected by several universities for study. When I get permission I will publish again in real voice audio.
